snippet.title: Actua Golf 2 Playstation Gameplay
snippet.description:
Here's something I haven't done in a while....golf.....and then I realised why it's been so long from I have done a golf game...let's leave it at that.

I wish to note that this was recorded before the Ryder Cup and before the death of Arnold Palmer which is why I haven't referenced either of them in this video.

Also, as I play a single player game and not against an opponent, this game does not count towards the Golf track record.
